{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>1. Different Ways to Breed Elite Horses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503710/extras/Breeding.png?t=1738742086\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can breed horses that focus on specific abilities. For example, to have a better draft horse, you can breed a baby horse from a stallion with a high stamina attribute and formulate a specific feed to increase its strength ability.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>2. Buy and Sell Horses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503710/extras/BuySell.png?t=1738742086\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy horses and start your business. Breed better and better horses, forge equipment for them, and then sell them for a good price. With a well-equipped and capable horse, you can make a lot of money.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>3. Forge Equipment and Weapons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503710/extras/Forge.png?t=1738742086\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Improve your skills and upgrade your smithy, forging different equipment and weapons to sell or use on your horse.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>4. The store</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503710/extras/store.png?t=1738742086\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sell \u200b\u200bthe equipment and weapons you forge in your store to attract more customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738742086","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503710/page.bg.jpg?t=1738